{"tid":1992563,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【天若有情】袁鳳瑛轉行被黑社會恐嚇 患抑鬱想自殺幸得一人出援","createTime":"2020-04-28T08:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T15:10:50.000Z","uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b2b392c115037c6b6ca469d03b12b683a18d3e42","tid":1992563,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9XgRuA1LjyQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9XgRuA1LjyQ&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=84e6f8d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9XgRuA1LjyQ</a><br />\n<br />\n憑《天若有情》而廣被認識的歌手袁鳳瑛近日接受新城電台節目《詩情廿四味》訪問，她直認自己過往的星途並未順利，更被形容為「古墓派掌門人」，她說：「我唔食煙、唔飲酒、唔講粗口、唔埋堆又唔趁墟，唔太鍾意吃喝玩樂，加上自己食素，好多飯局都難以參與。」她笑言當年被召喚不收分文獻唱《天若有情》，沒想到紅起來，後來獲羅大佑賞識簽約唱片公司，先後推出三個專輯，不過被羅大佑責罵她不會交際應酬，更發火掟煙灰缸。"},{"pid":"93623e6d124b1e17a99a118a696d8affe871cbaf","tid":1992563,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:26:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lVq43exlH_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlVq43exlH_s&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=89f7d7cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lVq43exlH_s</a><br />\n86 新秀歌唱"},{"pid":"8399a139cbe583c25ecc333dc0445237302a93bc","tid":1992563,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:26:53.000Z","msg":"袁鳳瑛深明自己不是不適合做歌手，於是離職開音樂教室，沒想到遇人不淑，與拍檔合作出現分歧，而對方有黑社會背景，不斷找人來對她作出恐嚇，揚言要向她淋漒水。後來，袁鳳瑛另起爐灶再開教室，該拍檔又找人去搗亂，破壞所有設備，學生家長都嚇到退學，開業短短幾個月就被迫關門大吉。袁鳳瑛表示自己2歲開始已經可以睇到人的前世今生，就算天上的天使、地獄的眾生都睇得到、感受到、聞到、聽到，她說：「其實好多天使在人間，同普通人一樣，只係形應同人有少少唔同。我知大家唔係第一身經歷，一定會好難明白，但呢個對我而言係好清晰，好真實，好多情況你係估都估唔到，就算睇好多劇集都演唔出千份之一。」"},{"pid":"9d8b05581ddfa4a5e0c2faaa8861110be6803056","tid":1992563,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:27:08.000Z","msg":"她看過自己跟這個拍檔幾世都有恩怨，始終命數難逃，她說：「呢個關口都幾重大，當時心情好低落，當時被黑社會不停騷擾，拍檔扮家長打電話上報館指我信邪教，又搵古惑仔去恐嚇我，我屋企成棟大廈都收到大字報，當時報警，警察唔受理，特別我係藝人，總係建議糾紛叫我哋自己解決。我當時真係想自殺，因為發現世界上連警察都幫唔到嘅時候，我覺得自己活喺地獄。幸好我信佛最後冇去自己，但抑鬱症發作，兩星期唔落床、唔刷牙唔洗臉，不過好神奇，以往我同哥哥關係不是太好，大家分開住，但有日佢突然搵我，決定扶我落街面對人群，鼓勵我重新做人。」"},{"pid":"e5752f7f2de53dad053af0dcd875ed41d46f7329","tid":1992563,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xZ-3P7amTao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxZ-3P7amTao&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=b0d7ed70\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xZ-3P7amTao</a>"},{"pid":"1a586fed7fc4c1d92b97f494f266b089997b6f6b","tid":1992563,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"09d1655bf6a918e057d9879a0991407623f609f2","tid":1992563,"uid":115910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"羅大佑食屎啦,唔應酬都要俾你屌"},{"pid":"0fe9ba5611923e0ea72b300ef35360ce2cdc4a21","tid":1992563,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c80c52bb209ef43405ef73e51443a92c24cf79","tid":1992563,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"09d1655bf6a918e057d9879a0991407623f609f2","tid":1992563,"uid":115910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"羅大佑食屎啦,唔應酬都要俾你屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"應酬包唔包比佢屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922776c178a3c88451226036638a01d2264832b4","tid":1992563,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6ba584212e5c27784e4ae2f154406cdbde149f43","tid":1992563,"uid":293801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:45:40.000Z","msg":"如果佢生存係今日，可能發展會好啲。起碼多咗好多網上平台，俾佢放自己唱嘅歌。"},{"pid":"b2b6c3e906bc489512ccad5d907568ea55d24336","tid":1992563,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09d1655bf6a918e057d9879a0991407623f609f2","tid":1992563,"uid":115910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"羅大佑食屎啦,唔應酬都要俾你屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"咩事<br />\n願聞其詳"},{"pid":"aa05a6d2e1da9ad4a86bcb0de34c02fcd32f447d","tid":1992563,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:25:15.000Z","msg":"如果唔係套電影真係冇乜邊個會識 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc489d2f210e14cc3ff10c6ce90525b1b307f02d","tid":1992563,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:10:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wRI2fZNP2zU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwRI2fZNP2zU&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=2cf0d349\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wRI2fZNP2zU</a><br />\n<br />\n未來偶像總決賽88<br />\n<br />\n86新秀落選後再戰未來偶像，獲得最突出台風獎"}]}